trans-unit.source: Provides <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement"></xref> objects for each state of the collapse button of a common group of items in the Explorer Bar.

Each property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ExplorerBar.NormalGroupCollapse> class gets a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> for a different state of the collapse button of a common group of items in the Explorer Bar, such as the **File and Folder Tasks** group in Windows Explorer.
Gets a visual style element that represents a hot collapse button of a common group of items in the Explorer Bar.

You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ExplorerBar.NormalGroupCollapse.Hot%2A> property to create a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer>.
A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement"></xref> that represents a hot collapse button.
Gets a visual style element that represents a normal collapse button of a common group of items in the Explorer Bar.

You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ExplorerBar.NormalGroupCollapse.Normal%2A> property to create a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer>.
A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement"></xref> that represents a normal collapse button.
Gets a visual style element that represents a pressed collapse button of a common group of items in the Explorer Bar.

You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ExplorerBar.NormalGroupCollapse.Pressed%2A> property to create a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer>.
A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement"></xref> that represents a pressed collapse button.
